headline: Bear of the Day: HubSpot (HUBS)
summary: Despite its established position as a CRM leader for small-to-medium-sized businesses, HubSpot currently faces a challenging crossroads. With the emergence of powerful, AI-driven alternatives, HubSpot's margins are likely to be threatened.
